DESCRIPTION:RAISED By TV brings you:SCHITTS CREEK Trivia Night!50 BRAND NEW
	 questions about your favorite Rose family misfits- covering all 6 seasons
	 Tues Mar 24th$7 ONLINE ADVANCE: {plus ticketing fees}$9 AT THE DOOR {plus
	 ticketing fees}Doors open at 6:00. Trivia starts at 7:00!Tables are first
	 come first serve.CLOCK-OUT is a 21 and over venue starting at 8pm **PRIZE
	S**The RAISED BY TV gang has put together some killer prize packages. Team
	s of 1-5 are welcome. Prizes for 1st\\\, 2nd\\\, t have to be good at triv
	ia just come on down to relive some Rose family shenanigans with us. **FOO
