	ees)\n\nAsher White:\n\nAs a multi-instrumentalist and producer\, Asher Wh
	ite’s auteurish pop vision is vulgar and transcendent: marrying skittering
	 noise with swooping strings\, lively banjo with blasts of feedback\, diss
	onant flutes with elegant bossa nova. Since the early 2010s she has develo
	ped a sprawling discography that spans experimental drone\, tropicalia\, n
	oise rock\, and folk.\n\nPlease note\, the Sunset Tavern is a strictly 21+
